-4">Downloading Option:</h3>
<p class=3D"sm:text-xl text-sm leading-[1.5rem] sm:leading-[2.2rem] mt-2">O=
nce the addresses are generated, you can click on the =E2=80=9CDownload=E2=
=80=9D button to save them all to your device in JSON or CSV format. Instea=
d of wasting time copying and pasting each of the addresses manually in a f=
ile to preserve them, you can use this feature to save time.</p>
